Good Hair;;69;;95;;PG-13;;Prompted by a question from his young daughter, comic Chris Rock sets out to explore the importance of hair in black culture. Rock interviews celebrities such as Ice-T and Raven Symone, and visits hair salons, stylist competitions and even an Indian temple to learn about hair culture.;;Documentary;;Jeff Stilson;;2009;;Chris Rock,Maya Angelou,Nia Long,Ice-T,Eve,Meagan Good,Andre Harrell,Melyssa Ford;;https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/good_hair